dmca.title: Notice and takedown letter regarding the infringing ici-i.biz domain name
dmca.body:
-----Original Message-----
From: Jennings, Patrick J. [mailto:patrick.jennings@pillsburylaw.com] 
Sent: Wednesday, March 21, 2007 3:34 PM
To: Copyright; Abuse
Subject: Notice and takedown letter regarding the infringing ici-i.biz
domain name
Importance: High

Dear Sirs,  

Attached please find a notice and take down letter pursuant to the
provisions of the Digital Millennium Copyright Act.  The letter details
infringement occurring on the Web site ici-i.biz.  We would appreciate
your prompt attention to this matter.

 <<ici-i.biz Notice and Takedown Letter.pdf>>  <<Ici-i.biz Exhibit
1.pdf>>  <<Ici-i.biz Exhibit 2.pdf>>  <<ici-i.biz Exhibit 3.pdf>>  
<<Ici-i.biz Exhibit 4.pdf>>  <<Ici-i.biz Exhibit 5.pdf>> 

Regards,

Patrick Jennings
